report that initialization of arma::SpMat objects through as<arma::spmat>()
in my package generated a memory management fault in valgrind for my
package, growfunctions.   The issue was sourced (not by me) and a fix was
incoporated at RcppArmadillo version 0.4.400 (and I am now using
