The c++filt tool is helpful:

  edd at max:~$ c++filt _ZTISo
  typeinfo for std::basic_ostream<char, std::char_traits<char> >
  edd at max:~$

This suggests basic iostream, ie C++ input/output. And indeed ...

| Best
